codeText: @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")_	protected Map<String, Object> extractMapFromMessage(MapMessage message) throws JMSException {_		Map<String, Object> map = new HashMap<>()__		Enumeration<String> en = message.getMapNames()__		while (en.hasMoreElements()) {_			String key = en.nextElement()__			map.put(key, message.getObject(key))__		}_		return map__	}
